abstract: |
  The Ipac-Nexus Framework is an early-stage, non-commercial architecture for real-time coordination of human well-being, designed to replace profit-based optimization with transparent, impact-driven resource allocation. This release serves as a conceptual blueprint and conversation starter, inviting critique, improvement, and interdisciplinary collaboration.
